## php Loops

## What are loops?
Loops are used to execute the same block of code multiple times.
Useful when repetition is required.

In simple terms: 
Run the same block of code again and again.

## Types of loops
1. for loop
--> Runs a block of code fixed number of times

2. foreach loop
--> Used for arrays
--> Runs once for each element

3. while loop
--> Runs as long as condition is true

4. do-while loop
--> Runs at least once, then checks condition
